Popular skit maker and Instagram comedian, Kelvin Anagbogu aka Lord Lamba has joined the long list of bachelors interested in billionaire heiress, Cuppy. The humour merchant via his Insta story said lately he’s been having recurrent dreams about the disc jockey. A few days ago, Lord Lamba revealed he is searching for a wife to complement his current status. He went on to highlight his accomplishments while asking God to bless him with a peaceful and understanding wife who would grow his wealth with him.   Reactions as Portable adorns suit for first time     PVCs should be substituted for show tickets, says…     Tonto Dikeh and I are neither friends nor enemies – Uche…   - Advertisement - “Man don make money. Man don buy cars. Man don get house. Baba God one last thing… a wife that would understand me and be my peace and we can make more money together,” he wrote. Following his request, the 26-year-old content creator has wondered if seeing DJ Cuppy in his dreams may just be the answer he prayed for. “This one I am just seeing DJ Cuppy in my dreams for the past two days now. Is this a sign hmmmmm,” he wrote.